_sText: AKs and M4s only.  CTs begin w/ M4s and have 6 flashbangs to use upon entry of the warehouse.  2 AWPs lay in the middle of the map along with grenades.  No armor was given to players to make it more of a "real damage" effect.  Also, ammo whores beware!  You only have 1 30 rnd magazine then you're either using your secondary, throwing nades, going melee, or stealing other guns from people that never spawned back at a spawn site.  Enjoy!
